</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-27_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-28_ pf-text-1"><strong>First aid</strong> - immediate assistance given to a person suffering from a minor or severe illness or injury to preserve life, prevent the condition from worsening, or promote recovery.
