</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-45_ pf-text-1"><strong>Assess the casualty</strong> - Without moving the casualty, quickly determine the number of injured individuals and the nature of their injuries.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-47_ pf-text-1"><strong>Call for help</strong> - Immediately notify emergency services if the situation is beyond simple first aid measures.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-49_ pf-text-1"><strong>Use protective gear</strong> - Utilise appropriate personal protective equipment (PPE) to prevent any transmission of infectious diseases.



